job.name: :android: CI build; gradle task: buildCheckTestWayfairDebug
job.command:
# Set artifact bucket
echo "--- :point_down: Downloding archived pipeline"

bucket="rt://buildkite-artifacts/$BUILDKITE_PIPELINE_SLUG/$BUILDKITE_JOB_ID"
echo "Setting artifact bucket to: ${bucket}"
export BUILDKITE_ARTIFACT_UPLOAD_DESTINATION=$bucket

if [ -n "${BUILDKITE_TRIGGERED_FROM_BUILD_ID}" ] && buildkite-agent artifact shasum "buildkite-android-app-ci.tar.gz" --build "${BUILDKITE_TRIGGERED_FROM_BUILD_ID}"; then
  buildkite-agent artifact download "buildkite-android-app-ci.tar.gz" . --build ${BUILDKITE_TRIGGERED_FROM_BUILD_ID}
elif [ -n "${BUILDKITE_BUILD_ID}" ] && buildkite-agent artifact shasum "buildkite-android-app-ci.tar.gz" --build "${BUILDKITE_BUILD_ID}"; then
  buildkite-agent artifact download "buildkite-android-app-ci.tar.gz" . --build ${BUILDKITE_BUILD_ID}
else
  exit 1
fi

tar -xzf buildkite-android-app-ci.tar.gz

# Run the CI build
PR_BRANCH=${BUILDKITE_BRANCH} ./buildkite-android-app-ci/buildkite/scripts/ci-generic.sh
